# Agent playbook — bundle release (local only)

**Canonical template:** [snippets/maintainer-local/AGENTS-LOCAL.md.example](snippets/maintainer-local/AGENTS-LOCAL.md.example)

```bash
./snippets/bootstrap-maintainer-local.sh
```

That copies the template to gitignored **`AGENTS-LOCAL.md`** in the bundle root.

See also [snippets/maintainer-local/README.md](snippets/maintainer-local/README.md).
